P_HTM[1628]='*888. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā upādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ? Kammassa katattā phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ āpodhātu – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā upādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1629]='*889. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā anupādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ? Na kammassa katattā phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ āpodhātu – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā anupādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1630]='*890. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā sappaṭighaṃ? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… rasāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā sappaṭighaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1631]='*891. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā  appaṭighaṃ? Itthindriyaṃ…pe… kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā appaṭighaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1632]='*892. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā sappaṭighaṃ? Phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā sappaṭighaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1633]='*893. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā appaṭighaṃ? Āpodhātu – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā appaṭighaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1634]='*894. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā oḷārikaṃ? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… rasāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā oḷārikaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1635]='*895. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā sukhumaṃ itthindriyaṃ…pe… kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā sukhumaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1636]='*896. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā oḷārikaṃ? Phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā oḷārikaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1637]='*897. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā sukhumaṃ? Āpodhātu – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ no upādā sukhumaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1638]='*898. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā dūre? Itthindriyaṃ…pe… kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā dūre.*';
P_HTM[1639]='*899. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ upādā santike? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… rasāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā santike.*';
