P_HTM[1643]='*903. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ anidassanaṃ? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… kāyāyatanaṃ, itthindriyaṃ purisindriyaṃ jīvitindriyaṃ, yaṃ vā panaññampi atthi rūpaṃ kammassa katattā  gandhāyatanaṃ rasāyatanaṃ phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ ākāsadhātu āpodhātu rūpassa upacayo rūpassa santati kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ anidassanaṃ.*';
