P_HTM[1647]='*907. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ appaṭighaṃ? Itthindriyaṃ purisindriyaṃ jīvitindriyaṃ, yaṃ vā panaññampi atthi rūpaṃ kammassa katattā ākāsadhātu āpodhātu rūpassa upacayo rūpassa santati kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ appaṭighaṃ.*';
