P_HTM[1658]='*918. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ dūre? Itthindriyaṃ purisindriyaṃ jīvitindriyaṃ, yaṃ vā panaññampi atthi rūpaṃ kammassa katattā ākāsadhātu āpodhātu rūpassa upacayo rūpassa santati kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ dūre.*';
P_HTM[1659]='*919. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ santike? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… kāyāyatanaṃ, yaṃ vā panaññampi atthi rūpaṃ kammassa katattā rūpāyatanaṃ gandhāyatanaṃ rasāyatanaṃ phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇaṃ santike.*';
P_HTM[1660]='*920. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ anupādiṇṇaṃ dūre? Kāyaviññatti  vacīviññatti rūpassa lahutā rūpassa mudutā rūpassa  kammaññatā rūpassa jaratā rūpassa aniccatā, yaṃ vā panaññampi atthi rūpaṃ na kammassa katattā ākāsadhātu āpodhātu rūpassa upacayo rūpassa santati kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ anupādiṇṇaṃ dūre.*';
P_HTM[1661]='*921. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ anupādiṇṇaṃ santike? Saddāyatanaṃ, yaṃ vā panaññampi atthi rūpaṃ na kammassa katattā rūpāyatanaṃ gandhāyatanaṃ rasāyatanaṃ phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ anupādiṇṇaṃ santike.*';
P_HTM[1662]='*922. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ sanidassanaṃ? Kammassa katattā rūpāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ sanidassanaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1663]='*923. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ anidassanaṃ? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… kāyāyatanaṃ, itthindriyaṃ purisindriyaṃ jīvitindriyaṃ, yaṃ vā panaññampi atthi rūpaṃ kammassa katattā gandhāyatanaṃ rasāyatanaṃ phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ ākāsadhātu āpodhātu rūpassa upacayo rūpassa santati kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ anidassanaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1664]='*924. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ anupādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ sanidassanaṃ? Na kammassa katattā rūpāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ anupādiṇṇupādāniyaṃ sanidassanaṃ.*';
