P_HTM[1683]='*943. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ sappaṭighaṃ na indriyaṃ? Rūpāyatanaṃ…pe… phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ sappaṭighaṃ na indriyaṃ.*';
