P_HTM[1685]='*945. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ appaṭighaṃ na indriyaṃ? Kāyaviññatti vacīviññatti…pe… kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ appaṭighaṃ na indriyaṃ.*';
