P_HTM[1687]='*947. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ sappaṭighaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… rasāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ sappaṭighaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ.*';
