P_HTM[1689]='*949. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ appaṭighaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ? Itthindriyaṃ…pe… kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ appaṭighaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ.*';
