P_HTM[1697]='*957. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na indriyaṃ santike? Rūpāyatanaṃ…pe… phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na indriyaṃ santike.*';
P_HTM[1698]='*958. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ oḷārikaṃ? Phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ oḷārikaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1699]='*959. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ sukhumaṃ? Āpodhātu – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ sukhumaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1700]='*960. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ oḷārikaṃ? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… rasāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ oḷārikaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1701]='*961. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ sukhumaṃ? Itthindriyaṃ…pe… kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ sukhumaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1702]='*962. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ dūre? Āpodhātu – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ dūre.*';
P_HTM[1703]='*963. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ santike? Phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ mahābhūtaṃ santike.*';
P_HTM[1704]='*964. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ dūre? Itthindriyaṃ…pe…  kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ dūre.*';
P_HTM[1705]='*965. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ santike? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… rasāyatanaṃ – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ na mahābhūtaṃ santike.*';
P_HTM[1706]='*966. Rūpāyatanaṃ diṭṭhaṃ, saddāyatanaṃ sutaṃ, gandhāyatanaṃ rasāyatanaṃ phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ mutaṃ, sabbaṃ rūpaṃ manasā viññātaṃ rūpaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1707]='*Evaṃ catubbidhena rūpasaṅgaho.*';
P_HTM[1708]='*Catukkaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1709]='*Pañcakaṃ*';
P_HTM[1710]='*967. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pathavīdhātu? Yaṃ kakkhaḷaṃ kharagataṃ *[kharigataṃ (ka.)]* kakkhaḷattaṃ kakkhaḷabhāvo ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā upādiṇṇaṃ vā anupādiṇṇaṃ vā – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pathavīdhātu.*';
P_HTM[1711]='*968. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ āpodhātu? Yaṃ āpo āpogataṃ sineho sinehagataṃ bandhanattaṃ rūpassa ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā upādiṇṇaṃ vā anupādiṇṇaṃ vā – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ āpodhātu.*';
P_HTM[1712]='*969. Katamaṃ  taṃ rūpaṃ tejodhātu? Yaṃ tejo tejogataṃ usmā usmāgataṃ usumaṃ usumagataṃ ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā upādiṇṇaṃ vā anupādiṇṇaṃ vā – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ tejodhātu.*';
P_HTM[1713]='*970. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ vāyodhātu? Yaṃ vāyo vāyogataṃ thambhitattaṃ rūpassa ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā upādiṇṇaṃ vā anupādiṇṇaṃ vā – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ vāyodhātu.*';
P_HTM[1714]='*971. Katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā? Cakkhāyatanaṃ…pe… kabaḷīkāro āhāro – idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ upādā.*';
P_HTM[1715]='*Evaṃ pañcavidhena rūpasaṅgaho.*';
P_HTM[1716]='*Pañcakaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1717]='*Chakkaṃ*';
P_HTM[1718]='*972. Rūpāyatanaṃ  cakkhuviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, saddāyatanaṃ sotaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, gandhāyatanaṃ ghānaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, rasāyatanaṃ jivhāviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ kāyaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, sabbaṃ rūpaṃ manoviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1719]='*Evaṃ chabbidhena rūpasaṅgaho.*';
P_HTM[1720]='*Chakkaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1721]='*Sattakaṃ*';
P_HTM[1722]='*973. Rūpāyatanaṃ  cakkhuviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, saddāyatanaṃ sotaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, gandhāyatanaṃ ghānaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, rasāyatanaṃ jivhāviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ kāyaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, rūpāyatanaṃ saddāyatanaṃ gandhāyatanaṃ rasāyatanaṃ phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ manodhātuviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, sabbaṃ rūpaṃ manoviññāṇadhātuviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1723]='*Evaṃ sattavidhena rūpasaṅgaho.*';
P_HTM[1724]='*Sattakaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1725]='*Aṭṭhakaṃ*';
P_HTM[1726]='*974. Rūpāyatanaṃ  cakkhuviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, saddāyatanaṃ sotaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, gandhāyatanaṃ ghānaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, rasāyatanaṃ jivhāviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, manāpiyo phoṭṭhabbo sukhasamphasso kāyaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, amanāpiyo phoṭṭhabbo dukkhasamphasso kāyaviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, rūpāyatanaṃ saddāyatanaṃ gandhāyatanaṃ rasāyatanaṃ phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṃ manodhātuviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ, sabbaṃ rūpaṃ manoviññāṇadhātuviññeyyaṃ rūpaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1727]='*Evaṃ aṭṭhavidhena rūpasaṅgaho.*';
